rule.description:
A list of reporting interfaces to be displayed on the Connected Onboarding trends page.

@customizable:1.0
@category:USER_INTERFACE
@app:FS.IO

rule.definition:
/*
DESCRIPTION: A list of reporting interfaces to be displayed on the Connected Onboarding trends page.
DEFAULT BEHAVIOR: By default, this interface returns a list of AS_FS_P_TrendsPageContent which contains only the OOTB interface, AS_IO_HCL_trendsReports, along with its visibility and a label in case more pages are added
CUSTOMIZATION STEPS: - Create any interfaces that should be displayed on the "Trends" tab of the site. NOTE: These interfaces must return a headerContentLayout and should not have any rule inputs. When testing your customization, if you receive the following error: "The baseHeaderContentLayout parameter must be defined as an instance of a!headerContentLayout", it means that your interface definition does not return an a!headerContentLayout() - For each of the pages to be displayed, add an instance of AS_FS_P_TrendsPageContent containing three fields: label - text shown in a radioButtonField for selecting the interface headerContentLayout - rule reference to the interface to be shown showWhen - defines the visibility of the interface - items with showWhen: false will be filtered out NOTE: If there are multiple visible interfaces for a user, a radioButtonField will automatically be shown at the top of the header which allows the user to switch interfaces using the "label" field. If there will only be one visible interface, a label is not needed. NOTE: The visibility of the trends tab as a whole is based on the combined visibility of all available pages here. - If you wish to remove the out of the box trends report entirely, you may do so.
PARAMETERS: i18nData
*/ { 'type!{urn:com:appian:types:AS:FS}AS_FS_P_TrendsPageContent'( /* Note: the label is not shown if there are fewer than 2 trends report pages to display for the user */ label: #"_a-0000e2cd-bc96-8000-9ba2-011c48011c48_81818"( i18nData: ri!i18nData, bundleKey: "AS.CO.AllBundles.lbl_DefaultTrendsInterface" ), /*define rule reference to interface here*/ headerContentLayout: #"_a-0000e471-623a-8000-9bc3-011c48011c48_734253", /*define interface visibility here*/ showWhen: #"urn:appian:function:v1:a:isusermemberofgroup?okey=a!isUserMemberOfGroup"( loggedInUser(), #"_a-0000e5da-4dac-8000-9ba5-011c48011c48_22793" ) ) }
